lead_paragraph: Jay Don Blake birdied three of the last five holes Thursday at windy Philadelphia Cricket Club for a 2-under 70 and the first-round lead in the Constellation Senior Players Championship.

headline.print_headline: Jay Don Blake Leads Senior Players Championship
